升级。 5 月 14 日一早，叶飞发布消息称，今天放出中源家居事件第一段录音，资料大概还要有几百个 G，涉及链条上的上市公司、券商、公募、私募、券商资管等。而除中源家居外，他还点名维信诺、昊志机电，并扬言公司还有很多。 上市公司市值管理究竟有着怎样的圈子？为何出现黑吃黑？而大 V 、券商以及私募等合谋操纵股价，又有怎样的套路？尽管事件浮现多重疑云，但业内人士告诉新京报贝壳财经记者，上市公司进行市值管理在业内并不罕见，而多方参与这一游戏常常是结局一地鸡毛。 「本身是拿不到桌面上的事，整个链条有很多风险和不确定性，有的就是靠信任。」业内人士告诉记者。新京报 - 好新闻，无止境"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "199 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/459558051"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8In9O3z+Wpx70wEAMaCDY0NDA0MjA1IL/X/YQGMAI4gQJADHIJNDU5NTU4MDUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1621131000.095496", "card_id": "Q_452808080", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "比特币牛市是否已过？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ce0b3e0f23d7176a5acd4925a0f9a876_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "196 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452808080"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8In9O3z+Wpx70wEAMaCDYyOTAzNTkxINTco4MGMAA46gFADXIJNDUyODA4MDgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1621131000.095862", "card_id": "Q_459492278", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 90}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待魅族 16 系列 5 月 15 日基本都出现大部分应用闪退问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b143a24dcab01d65548615f9342ef3c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "184 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/459492278"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8In9O3z+Wpx70wEAMaCDY0Mzg5NTczIJPg+oQGMAg4sAFADnIJNDU5NDkyMjc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1621131000.0962176", "card_id": "Q_297417967", "feed